# Waitlist destination — Formspree form endpoint.
#
# 1. Create a free form at https://formspree.io/
# 2. Copy its endpoint URL (looks like https://formspree.io/f/abcdwxyz)
# 3. For local dev: copy this file to .env.local and paste the URL below.
# 4. For production: add the same variable in Vercel
#    (Project Settings -> Environment Variables).
WAITLIST_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=
